description.oldValue:
Bringing a new way to navigate OneNote. Choose between the horizontal tabs at the top for your sections with notebooks and pages being separate on the side or a new navigation that consolidates notebooks, sections, and pages on the side and removes the tabs at the top.
GA date: April CY2023
